\id 2PE - Mbula
\h 2 Bitǝrus
\toc3 2Bit
\toc2 2 Bitǝrus
\toc1 2 Bitǝrus
\mt2 Ɓaria Cauterǝa mala
\mt1 BITƏRUS
\imt1 Mǝncau
\im \bk Ɓaria Cauterǝa mala Bitǝrus \bk* ka à gìlǝì aban ká a ban amǝkwaɗi arǝ a'ikǝlisiya pas ɓara-ɓara mǝnana à kutia ɓá ɓosǝkiban mala amǝ'ɓangnǝa mǝ'nyirì ka. Amǝnia yia amǝ'ɓangnǝa mǝ'nyirì ka, aɓwana na aɓalǝ amǝkwaɗi. À kutia kanigir mana kyanggi kanigir andǝ nggurcau mǝ'mǝsǝcau nì, mana à kùmô a bu amǝ'mishan mǝdǝmbe; yia amǝ'mishan mǝnana nǝ nggearǝia ka à sǝn Yesu sǝ à ok kanigir a kúni ka. Ɓariki mala mǝgilǝgir ka, kǝ earce tamsǝ túró mala amǝ kanigir nyirì man andǝ kiɗìkì mǝnana nǝ̀ yiu aɓa kanigir malea ka. Yia amǝ kanigir nyirì ka à tsǝk aɓea amǝkwaɗi à kutia ndali nǝ man tsǝa sǝ ba ado Kǝrǝsti malaká nyar raka, ɓǝ̀ kàngkàng nǝ̀ nyare nǝ̀ yiu ka. Mǝgilǝgir bǝlɓalǝi ama Mǝtalabangŋo ka kǝ dǝndi arǝ nyare male ɗang, sǝama nda rǝ pak munyi ace nyinggi koyan ngga njar ɓǝ̀ pǝlǝ nzǝmi arǝ acauɓikea male ɓǝ̀ pwanzali (\xt 2Bit 3:9\xt*.) Mǝgilǝgir kwarkir amǝkwaɗi ɓǝa dukdo mǝnana nǝ̀ pwasǝbum Ɓakuli ka. Amur mǝnana à nǝ̀ nggǝ kwaki kiria arǝ cau ɓalkiɓabum mǝnana à kwakia aɓa kutan ngga, amǝkwaɗi ɓǝa tsǝk ɗenyicau pepe arǝ cau mala Yesu sǝ ɓǝa nying Bangŋo Mǝfele ɓǝ̀ gingnǝ ɓabumia.
\iot Agir mǝnana aɓalǝi ka
\io1 Tita cau\ior 1:1-2\ior*
\io1 Wu pwasǝbum Ɓakuli sǝ wu bwal kàngkàng arǝ Mǝsǝcau\ior 1:3-21\ior*
\io1 Wu yál rǝ wun arǝ Amǝ ɓangnǝa Mǝ'nyirì andǝ Amǝ kanigir Mǝ'nyirì\ior 2:1-22\ior*
\io1 Wu do aɓa gilǝrǝu acemǝnana Mǝtalabangŋo nǝ̀ yiu\ior 3:1-16\ior*
\io1 Masǝlǝata kwarkiru\ior 3:17-18\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Makkun
\p 
\v 1 Makkun mǝnana pur nǝ bu Shiman Bitǝrus, guro sǝ mǝ'mishan mala Yesu Kǝrǝsti.
\p Aban ká aban aɓwana mǝnana à kumǝna paɓamuru kǝla mǝnana sǝm ndanǝi ka, atàcau mala ɓealɓoarna mala Ɓakuli andǝ Mǝ'amsǝ sǝm Yesu Kǝrǝsti.
\p 
\v 2 Ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli pa wun ɓwamuru andǝ dorǝpwala kam kpǝm nǝ lidǝmba ma'wun aɓa súrǝ̀ Ɓakuli andǝ Yesu Mǝtala sǝm.
\s1 Do mala amǝkpata Kǝrǝsti
\p 
\v 3 Ɓakuli aɓa rǝcandǝa male ka pana sǝm koya gìr mǝnana ɓoaro ɓǝ̀ sǝm pang nǝi ace do yilǝmu andǝ do ɓanggi Ɓakuli ka. Amǝnia yì agir ka Ɓakuli pà sǝmia kat lang sǝm yì súrǝ̀ Yesu mǝnana tunǝ sǝm ɓǝ̀ sǝm kum kāmbe aɓa gulo andǝ ɓoaro male ka.
\v 4 Sǝ atàcau mala gulo andǝ ɓoaro male ka, ɓwamur sǝm pà sǝm aɓoro amǝgulke kǝ̀rkǝ́r andǝ amǝɓoarne mǝnana bang ama nǝ̀ pà ka. Pak mǝnia ka ace mǝnana nǝ amǝnia yì aɓoro ka, ɓǝ̀ sǝm kum kāmbe aɓa pa male mala do Ɓakuli, sǝ ɓǝ̀ sǝm apî kiɗikiban mala ɓanza mǝnana suno mǝɓane kǝ yinǝi ka.
\p 
\v 5 Ace mǝnia ka, wu ɓariki, wu lùmsǝkún paɓamuru ma'wun nǝ pěmǝɓoarne; sǝ pěmǝɓoarne ka wu gbashite nǝ súrǝ̀gir;
\v 6 súrǝ̀gir ka wu gbashite nǝ bwalrǝu; bwalrǝu ka wu gbashite nǝ gandǝrǝu; gandǝrǝu ka wu gbashite nǝ do ɓanggi Ɓakuli.
\v 7 Sǝ do ɓanggi Ɓakuli ka wu gbashite nǝ ɗenyi nǝ aɓwana kǝla amǝ'eamrǝarǝu andǝ lǝmdǝ earcearǝu aban koyan ngga.
\v 8 Ɓǝ̀ wu ndanǝ amǝnia yì aɓealu, sǝ à nǝ̀ nggǝ gul aɓalǝ wun ngga, pa wu nǝ̀ gatti aɓalǝ atúró ɗang, sǝ súrǝ̀gir ma'wun amur Mǝtala sǝm Yesu Kǝrǝsti ka, nǝ̀ duk gir mǝɓoarne andǝ gbasha aban aɓwana.
\v 9 Sǝ ɓwa mǝnana pànǝ amǝnia yì aɓealu raka, dumǝna nte, kǝ sǝnban kuko ɗàng, sǝ ɓālǝi lorǝna ama à langŋǝ́nì wi acauɓikea male mǝ'ɗiɗyali.
\p 
\v 10 Acemani ka, wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu, wu pà rǝcandǝa arǝ lǝmdǝí ama ɓafo na wu nda aɓalǝ aɓwana mǝnana Ɓakuli tunǝia, sǝ tarkia ka. Ɓǝ̀ wu lidǝmba nǝ do aɓalǝ amǝno yì aɓealu ka, pà wu nǝ̀ kútí aɓa cauɓikea ɗang, sǝ paɓamuru ma'wun ngga nǝ̀ kum kusǝu came.
\v 11 Anggo ka, sǝ Ɓakuli nǝ̀ mǝnba wun kunɓala wyang ace kutio aɓa Domurǝm mala Mǝtala sǝm andǝ Mǝ'amsǝ sǝm yì Yesu Kǝrǝsti, Domurǝm male mǝnana masǝlǝate pà kàm raka.
\s1 Tsǝkiru arǝ cau mala Malǝmce
\p 
\v 12 Ace mani ka, mǝ ndanǝi a ɓabumam mǝ nggǝ kasǝɓalǝ wun koya pwari arǝ amǝnia yì acau ka, kat andǝ amani ama wu súrǝ́nia, sǝ wu tamsǝna kusǝ wun kàngkàng amur mǝsǝcau mǝnana wu angŋǝni ka.
\v 13 Yàle a sǝne mem ngga, aɓa do mem kat aɓa mǝnia yì nggūrǝu ka, ɓoaro ɓǝn nggǝ kasǝɓalǝ wun.
\v 14 Ən sǝlǝna ama pà nǝ̀ sau ɗang mǝ ndo mǝ nǝ ɗeki mǝnia yì do ɓanza ka, kǝla mǝnana Mǝtala sǝm Yesu Kǝrǝsti angŋǝna dǝmba lǝ́mdǝ́nàm ngga.
\v 15 Sǝ mǝ nǝ ɓariki a koya njar ka, mǝ nǝ pak gìr mǝnana nǝ̀ tsǝa anzǝm mǝnana ǝn umǝna ka, ɓalǝ wun ɓǝ̀ kǝ kasǝa rǝ amǝnia yì agir ka ko aya pwari.
\s1 Cau amur ɓoarɓwa mala Kǝrǝsti
\p 
\v 16 Cau mǝnana sǝm bangga wun amur rǝcandǝa andǝ yiu mala Mǝtala sǝm Yesu Kǝrǝsti ka, sǝm pà aban bangga wun njarnzǝne mǝnana ɓeɓwa pusǝì aɓa kutan ngga ɗàng. Nǝ nggearǝ mǝsǝ sǝm, sǝm sǝn tǎ mala ɓoarɓwa male.
\v 17 Sǝm nda kam à kǝ banì mǝnana Ɓakuli Tárrú pe wi ɓoarɓwa andǝ gulo, pǝlǝa gi Ɓakuli pur nǝ ɓá mǝno yì tǎ mǝgule mala ɓoarɓwa ka, yiu a baní ama, <<Mǝnia ka, nda Munem mǝnana ǝn nggǝ earce ka, kǝ pwasǝ bumam kǝ̀rkǝ́r.>>
\v 18 Nggearǝ sǝm ngga, sǝm ok mǝno yì giu pur nǝ kuli ka, acemǝnana sǝm nda kam atè amur nkono mǝfele.\f + \fr 1:18 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Mat 17:1-5; Mar 9:2-7; Luk 9:28-35\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 19 Amur mani ka, sǝm ndanǝ mǝsǝkang-kangŋa mǝnana kútì mǝno ka ama, cau mǝnana amǝ'ɓangnǝa hamnǝi ka mǝsǝcau na. Nǝ̀ dumnǝ ɓoaro, ɓǝ̀ wu tsǝkir wun arǝì, kǝla mǝnana wun nǝ̀ tsǝkir wun arǝ pitǝla mana kǝ tá aɓa pǝndǝa bà kwaro mala ban, sǝ nlero dǝmbari yi tana a ɓabum wun ngga.
\v 20 Gìr mǝnana kutibanì kat ka, wu sǝlǝ ama ɓekǝ ɓangnǝa pa kàm aɓa Malǝmce mǝnana pur nǝ ɓá mǝngicau mala mǝɓangnǝa ka ɗàng.
\v 21 Acemǝnana na gi Ɓakuli ka, kǝ pur aɓa kani mala mǝɓangnǝa ɗang. Amǝno yì amǝ'ɓangnǝa ka, Bangŋo Mǝfele na gingnǝia sǝ à nacau mǝnana pur nǝban Ɓakuli ka.
\c 2
\s1 Amǝ'ɓangnǝa andǝ amalǝm mǝ'nyirì
\p 
\v 1 Sǝ amǝ'ɓangnǝa mǝ'nyirì gbal ka à lo aɓalǝ amǝ Isǝrayila, sǝ kǝla mǝno ka amǝkànìgìr mǝ'nyirì nǝ̀ nggá lo aɓalǝ wun. Aɓa kutan à nǝ̀ yiu nǝ akanìgìr mǝ'nyirì mǝnana à nǝ̀ kiɗikina paɓamuru mala aɓwana nǝia ka, yàle à nǝ̀ tǝmce Mǝtalabangŋo mǝnana akmúr sǝm aɓalǝ acauɓikea ma'sǝm ngga. Anggo sǝ à nǝ̀ nunbi ɓamuria kiɗikiban a kaurǝa.\f + \fr 2:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Yahu 1:4-6\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 2 Aɓwana pas nǝ̀ kpata kusǝia mala do kìɗìkì mala nongginǝ-rǝarǝu, sǝ ace amǝnia yì amǝkànìgìr mǝ'nyirì ka, aɓwana nǝ̀ ɓǝsǝki ce njar mala mǝsǝcau.
\v 3 Nzumon malea nǝ̀ cia à nǝ̀ yiu nǝ acau swarkiban aɓa kutan, à nǝ̀ ɓǝmbǝri wun. Ɓakuli angŋǝna dǝmba ɗiɗyal kasǝnia ɓashi, sǝ kiɗikea malea ka, ceì nong ɗang.
\p 
\v 4 Nggearǝ amǝturonjar mǝnana à pak cauɓikea ka, Ɓakuli sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr malea ɗàng, ramtea aɓa nggea tūli-bǝsa, kùrkia kam a ban mǝpǝndǝe mǝnana kǝlling-kǝlling ngga, sheɓǝ̀ pwari pak ɓashi pangŋǝ̀nà ka.\f + \fr 2:4 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Sǝn 20:2-3,10\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 5 Sǝ aɓwana mǝnana a ɓanza mana ɗiɗyal ka, Ɓakuli sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr malea ɗàng, she kǝ Nuhu mǝ hamnǝ cau mala do-ɓealɓoarna andǝ aɓea aɓwana tongno-nong-ɓari na. Ɓakuli amsǝia a bàkú mǝnana yiu nǝ nggea mùr-gùla amur ɓanza mala amǝ'cauɓikea ka.\f + \fr 2:5 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 8:18; 6:6-8\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 6 Ɗǝm ngga Ɓakuli ɓashia anggea-là mala amǝ Sodom andǝ mala amǝ Gomora, pisǝia à pǝlǝ agìgí mala tú. Pǝlǝa cia à duk girkani arǝ gir mǝnana nǝ̀ kum amǝ ɗwanyi kpata Ɓakuli ka.\f + \fr 2:6 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 19:24\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 7 Sǝ Lotu mǝnana mǝɓealɓoarna na ka Ɓakuli amsǝi aɓa Sodom. Ɓakuli amsǝi acemǝnana yì ka, kútí aɓa ɗwanyi banɓoarnado andǝ bumkiɗikea arǝ do kìɗìkì mala nongginǝban mala amǝ'ɓealɓikea.\f + \fr 2:7 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 19:1-16\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 8 Aɓa do mala mǝno yì ɓwa mǝɓoarne yì Lotu, aɓalǝ amǝ'ɓealɓikea ka, kum tanni kǝ̀rkǝ́r aɓa yilǝmi nǝ ɓealɓikea mana kǝ sǝni nǝ mǝsǝì, sǝ kǝ oe nǝ kiri a koya pwari ka.
\v 9 Mǝtalabangŋo ka súrǝ́nà njar mana nǝ̀ amsǝna amǝ'ɓealɓoarna nǝi aɓalǝ akārǝkiban malea, sǝ amǝ'ɓealɓikea ka, nǝ̀ cia aɓata tanni, bà pwari mala ɓashi.
\v 10 Nggeamurǝmi ka, nǝ̀ ɓashi amǝ gyata kìɗìkì mala anpel mala nggūrǝu, andǝ amǝ būrǝce yálban mala Ɓakuli amúrià.
\p Acemǝnana amǝnia yì amǝkànìgìr mǝ'nyirì ka à ndanǝ gusǝlǝ-ɓamuru, andǝ candǝ-ɓamuru ɗǝm ngga, ko ɓangciu kǝ pakkia wia arǝ na mǝɓane amur amǝturonjar a kùli, mǝnana Ɓakuli pea wia tǎ aɓa ɓoarɓwa ka ɗàng.
\v 11 Sǝ kat andǝ amani ama yia amǝturonjar ka à kútì aɓwana mǝnia nǝ rǝcandǝa andǝ gulo ka, à kǝ loasǝ kunia ama à nǝ̀ na mǝɓane amúrià aɓa ká nǝ cauɓashi a ɓadǝm Ɓakuli ka ɗàng.
\v 12 Amǝnia yì amǝkànìgìr mǝ'nyirì ka, à kǝ gyata oě malea a rǝǔ, kǝla anyamɓikea mǝnana à pànǝ ɗenyicau raka, mana à pusǝia ace bwalia ɓǝà wallia ka. À kǝ na mǝɓane amur gìr mǝnana à bwalta kusǝì raka, sǝ acemǝnana à nda kǝla agirkusǝu ka, à nǝ̀ kiɗikia.
\p 
\v 13 Kiɗikea malea ka, tangnakusǝia na ace ɓealɓikea mǝnana à lǝmdǝí ka. Do kìɗìkì mala likiali andǝ nukiagir nǝ nggea pwari a kùli ka, à nyesǝi banɓoarnado na a bania. A ban likwar atà wun ngga à duk agir kǝsǝkya andǝ agir ɓǝsǝkiban aɓalǝ wun, à panzǝ rǝia arǝ pak banɓoarnado nǝ pakkiagir ɓosǝkiban malea.
\v 14 Rǝia kǝ ɓǝla nǝ suno nong nǝ amamǝna ko aburana mǝnana à pà doɓala andǝia raka, sǝ ko à kǝ aulǝ nǝ pak cauɓikea ɗang. À kǝ swár aɓwana mǝnana kusǝia cam raka aban ká pak cauɓikea. Ɓabumia kwár aɓa nzumon. Yia ka aɓwana na aɓata súban mala Ɓakuli.
\v 15 À nyìngŋǝ̀nà njar mala mǝsǝcau sǝ à ɓwarkini tanjar mǝɓoarne. À kpanatà njar mala Bil'am muna mala Beyo, mǝnana earce kum boalo nǝ njar gir mala cauɓikea ka.\f + \fr 2:15 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ɓal 22:4-35\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 16 Sǝ yì ka, dambǝritso gimbi arǝ túró mǝɓike male; dambǝritso mǝnana girkusǝu nda kǝ nacau raka, bangcau nǝ gi ɓwapǝndǝa sǝ tamsǝ ɓangya mala mǝɓangnǝa.\f + \fr 2:16 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ɓal 22:21,23,28,30-31\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 17 Amǝnia yì aɓwana ka, à dumǝna agir mǝɓane kǝla amgbeɗe mǝnana à imǝna ka, ko kǝla burambulo mǝnana gung loasǝi ka. Ɓakuli gilǝkina ban acea a nggea ɓá pǝndǝa mǝlime.
\v 18 Nǝ́ naki acau mǝɓange mala twàlɓamúrû malea, à kǝ swár aɓwana mǝnana à ndarǝ puro à nǝ̀ apî ɓalǝ aɓwana mǝnana a do aɓa ɓwarkio mala cauɓikea ka. À kǝ ɓariki à nǝ̀ nunnia aɓalǝ asuno mǝɓane mala nggūrǝ ɓwapǝndǝa mǝ'earce kìɗìkì mala cauɓikea.
\v 19 Amǝnia yì amǝkànìgìr mǝ'nyirì ka à kǝ nea aɓwana mǝnia ama à nǝ̀ pea wia kum-ɓamúrû, sǝ yia nǝ ɓamuria ka, à nda ka guro mala aɓealu mala kìɗìkì. Gìr mǝnana kat limurǝm amur ɓwa ka, ɓwe pǝlǝna guro aɓata gìr nî.
\v 20 Sǝ ɓǝà ɓwana apini aɓealɓikea mala ɓanza nǝ njargula súrǝ̀ Mǝtala sǝm andǝ Mǝ'amsǝ sǝm Yesu Kǝrǝsti, sǝ à nyar ɗǝm nǝnzǝ́mò à yì marǝki rǝia sǝ à ɓungio aɓalǝ aɓealɓikea mǝno ka, zuriki mǝnana à nda aɓalǝi ado ka, ɓikina kutina mǝdǝmbe.
\v 21 Ɗwanyi súrǝ̀ njar mala do ɓealɓoarna malea ka ɓǝ́ ɓoarǝni banì amur mǝnana à sùrǝ́nì sǝ à pǝlǝ nzǝmia arǝ nzongcau mǝfele mǝnana à pea wia ka.
\v 22 Yia ka, à lǝmdǝna mǝsǝcau mala mǝnia yì kun-nacau mana ama,
\q1 <<Nvwa nyarǝna a li gìr
\q2 mǝnana ukki ka.>>\f + \fr 2:22 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pas 26:11\xt*\ft .\f*
\q1 <<Tǝmbǝrǝm ɓala mana
\q2 à sussǝi ka,
\q1 nyarǝna a ban tapiki
\q2 a dǝɓang.>>
\c 3
\s1 Nyare mala Mǝtalabangŋo
\p 
\v 1 Wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu, mǝnia ka nda ɓaria cauterǝa mem aban ká aban wun. Aɓalǝia kǝm ngga, ǝn ɓariki mǝ nǝ kasǝɓalǝ wun arǝ agir mǝnana wu súrǝ́nia, sǝ mǝ loasǝ aɗenyicau mǝɓoarne aɓalǝ wun.
\v 2 Ən nggǝ earce nǝma ɓǝ̀ wu ɗenyi nǝ acau mǝnana amǝ'ɓangnǝa mǝfele mala Ɓakuli bangŋi a pwarian, sǝ ɓalǝ wun ɓǝ̀ kǝa lórǝ́ nzongcau mǝnana Mǝtalabangŋo, Mǝ'amsǝban pá nǝ bu amǝ'mishan ma'wun ngga ɗang.
\p 
\v 3 Gir mǝnana wu nǝ̀ sǝlǝa a dǝmbe ka, nda mǝnana ama, a masǝlǝata apwari ka, amǝ'oalban nǝ̀ yia pusǝ rǝia, à nǝ̀ nggǝ oal mǝsǝcau, sǝ à nǝ̀ nggǝ kpata suno malea mǝ'cauɓike.
\v 4 À nǝ̀ na ama, <<Mǝtalabangŋo pacau ama nǝ̀ nyare nǝ̀ yiu re? Sǝ nda ake? Twal a pwarian ɓara-ɓara, aká sǝm yì wukio, sǝ agir kat ka à ndakam àkǝ̀ banì kǝla mǝnana à pusǝia atadǝmbe ka, kǝgìr nggaɗi ɗang.>>
\v 5 Kpakpak sǝ à būrǝce mǝnia yì mǝsǝcau ama ɓara-ɓara Ɓakuli pusǝ kuli andǝ agir mǝnana aɓalǝi ka, andǝ nzali nǝ nzongcau male mǝnana ne ka, sǝ tsǝk nzali pur aɓa mùr, sǝ nǝ mùr sǝ pak nzali.\f + \fr 3:5 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 1:6-9; 7:11\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 6 Pǝlǝa pak túró nǝ mǝnia yì mùr, yì nggea mùr-gùla ka, sǝ kiɗiki ɓanza mǝ'e.
\v 7 Nǝ́ kǝ cau mǝ'mwashati ka, kùli andǝ ɓanza mana ado ndakam ngga, cia nǝ tsǝa ace kiɗikia nǝ bǝsa. À cia nǝ tsǝa ace pwari ɓashi mǝnana Ɓakuli nǝ̀ kiɗiki aɓwana mana à pànǝ ulang do male raka.
\p 
\v 8 Sǝ ce ɓalǝ wun lórǝ́ mǝnia yì gir mwashat ka ɗàng, wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu: Pwari mwashat aban Mǝtalabangŋo ka, nda kǝla apǝlǝa á-mwashat, sǝ apǝlǝa á-mwashat ka, nda kǝla pwari mwashat.\f + \fr 3:8 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ang 90:4\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 9 Mǝtalabangŋo kǝ dǝndi arǝ lùmsǝ pacau male, kǝla mana aɓea ɓwana kǝ twali ka ɗàng. Awo, yì ka, ndanǝ munyi ace wun. Eare ama ɓǝ̀ kǝ ɓwa ɓǝ̀ kìɗìkì ɗàng. Eare male ka koyan ngga, ɓǝ̀ pwanzali ɓǝ̀ pǝlǝ nzǝmi arǝ acauɓikea male.
\p 
\v 10 Sǝama pwari mala Mǝtalabangŋo ka, nǝ̀ yiu kǝla yiu mala mǝn'í. A pwari mǝno ka kùli nǝ̀ ndǝrmya nǝ gǝggǝli mǝcandǝe, sǝ agir mǝnana a kùli ka à nǝ̀ pì kǝring a bǝsa, à nǝ̀ kiɗikea, sǝ ɓanza andǝ atúró mǝnana aɓalǝi ka à nǝ̀ nong kwas.\f + \fr 3:10 \fq à nǝ̀ nong kwas: \ft aɓea gilǝgir mǝnana à nyoulia nǝ bu ka, ama \fq à nǝ̀ pì kǝring; \ft aɓea ka ama \fq à nǝ̀ kiɗikea.\f*\f + \fr 3:10 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Mat 24:43; Luk 12:39; 1Tas 5:2; Sǝn 16:15\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 11 Sǝ acemǝnana koya gìr nǝ̀ kiɗiki anggo ka, ya ulang aɓwana na ɓoaro ɓǝ̀ sǝm pǎ? Ɓoaro ɓǝ̀ sǝm do aɓa do mǝfele andǝ do ulang mǝnana Ɓakuli earkiyice ka!
\v 12 Ɓǝ̀ sǝm dukdo kundǝ pwari mala Ɓakuli, andǝ ɓariki arǝ túró ace tsǝk yiu male ɓǝ̀ pa a kaurǝa.\f + \fr 3:12 \fq andǝ ɓariki arǝ túró ace tsǝk yiu male ɓǝ̀ pa a kaurǝa: \ft ko <<andǝ do nǝ rǝɓǝla arǝ earce yiu male.>>\f* A mǝno yì pwari ka, à nǝ̀ kiɗiki abumkuli nǝ bǝsa, sǝ agir mǝnana à nda a bumkuli ka, à nǝ̀ panzǝa aɓa pì mala bǝsa.\f + \fr 3:12 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Isha 34:4\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 13 Sǝ sǝm ngga, sǝm nda ban kundǝ kùli mǝbǝshe andǝ ɓanza mǝbǝshe mǝnana lùmsǝ nǝ ɓealɓoarna mala Ɓakuli, kǝla mǝnana bang ama nǝ̀ yinǝi ka.\f + \fr 3:13 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Isha 65:17; 66:22; Sǝn 21:1\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 14 Acemani ka, wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu, mǝno ado wu nda aban kundǝ amǝnia yì agir ɓǝà yiu ka, wu ɓariki wu do aɓa ɓoarnsari, andǝ ɗwanyicau-arǝǔ, sǝ wu dukdo rǝpwala.
\v 15 Wu ɗenyi ama, munyi mala Mǝtalabangŋo ka, nda rǝ pe ɓwapǝndǝa dǝmbu ɓǝ̀ kum amsǝban. Mǝnia ka, nda gìr mǝnana mǝ'eamrǝarǝu Bulǝs gbal ka gilǝa wun nǝ sǝlǝe mǝnana Ɓakuli pe wi ka.
\v 16 Kǝ nacau amur amǝnia yì agir ka aɓalǝ acauterǝa male kat. Aɓea cau male ka, súrǝè kwan kǝ̀rkǝ́r, sǝ aɓwana mǝnana à ɗwanyi sǝlǝe sǝ à kǝ came amur cau mǝ'mwashati raka, à kǝ pūrǝ acauterǝa male a mgbasho aban ká kìɗìkì malea, kǝla mǝnana à kǝ pak nǝ cili Amalǝmce ka. Mǝnia ka, nda gìr mǝnana nǝ̀ nunbia wia nggea kiɗikea mǝgule ka.
\s1 Masǝlǝata cau mala Bitǝrus
\p 
\v 17 Wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu, mǝno ado wu angŋa dǝmba wu sùrǝ́nà rǝ mǝnia ka, wu tsǝkir wun, ɓǝ̀ ɓwarkio mala amǝ'ɓealɓikea mǝnia ka ɓǝ̀ kǝa gǝshi wun a bancame ma'wun, ɓǝ̀ kyan nǝ wun a kpa ɗang.
\v 18 Wun ngga, wu lidǝmba nǝ gulo aɓa ɓwamuru andǝ súrǝ̀ Mǝtala sǝm andǝ Mǝ'amsǝ sǝm Yesu Kǝrǝsti. Gulo kat ka, male na, ado, andǝ mǝnana málá male pà kàm raka. Ɓǝ̀ do anggo.
